org.dotplot.core

Packages that use org.dotplot.core
org.dotplot Provides an entrypoint into the dotplot-system. 
org.dotplot.core Provides the core of the dotplot-system. 
org.dotplot.core.system Provides the Core-Plugin. 
org.dotplot.eclipse The core of the Plugin. 
org.dotplot.eclipse.actions Provides the actions to plot and to configure a plot and related classes. 
org.dotplot.eclipse.preferences configured plot. 
org.dotplot.eclipse.views Holds all GUI relevant classes: complete views, label providers and supporting classes. 
org.dotplot.fmatrix F-Matrix classes.
